howItWorks: |
  <h2>How this fire pit gravel calculator works</h2>
  <p>The calculator estimates the area of a circle, subtracts the inner fire pit area if needed, then multiplies by gravel depth to estimate volume.</p>
  <h2>Best gravel depth for fire pit areas</h2>
  <p>Decorative fire pit seating areas often use about 2 inches of gravel, though deeper layers may be needed for weed control, drainage, or leveling.</p>
